{"tid":2023844,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"派對場地協會對延長停業感奇怪 不理解政府衡量標準","createTime":"2020-05-19T09:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T09:29:02.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a5833a9285119dcd23b4eb60a6476ed5199bc216","tid":2023844,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"派對場地協會對延長停業感奇怪 不理解政府衡量標準<br />\n2020-05-19 HKT 17:04<br />\n<br />\n政府宣布，卡拉OK、派對房間、夜總會、浴室的停業安排，將延長7日，至本月28日，至於「限聚令」就延長14日，至6月4日。香港派對場地協會會長林漢然對政府的決定感到不可思議和奇怪，完全不理解政府是用甚麼標準來衡量停業安排。<br />\n<br />\n林漢然表示，其他已恢復營業的行業，例如戲院，酒吧等防疫措施，派對房間都可以跟隨，甚至做得更嚴緊，他們可以控制房間人數，要求客人戴口罩及禁止在房間進食，他不明白為何其他行業可以恢復，但派對房間就不可以。<br />\n<br />\n他說，過去一段時間，曾找區議員協助，又曾電郵不同部門，提出建議，但政府的回覆只「打官腔」。他表示，行內已有7至8成公司要結業賣盤，政府早前給予的每間公司4萬元資助，根本無補於事，如果資助不加碼，再停業多7日，只會有更多公司被迫結業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527065-20200519.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527065-20200519.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2Fx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=854e57a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527065-20200519.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e73bc259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527065-20200519.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">派對房間RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9f4c62a283b41a0badc9629faa48645ee73714a9","tid":2023844,"uid":50719,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:11:07.000Z","msg":"玩尻你，完。"},{"pid":"9aea06b82fd66b2bbaec3f795eef28576cc85834","tid":2023844,"uid":1327,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:12:25.000Z","msg":"做party room = 後生仔 =/